    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-10-04T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-10-04T00:00:00-05:00" n="664" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d664">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Hunter</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                                Tassara</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-10-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">October</hi> 4, 1865.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The undersigned, Acting Secretary of State of the United States, has the
                            honor to acknowledge the receipt of the note of Mr. Tassara, of the 26th
                            ultimo, relating to the late insurgent ram Stonewall, at Havana, and to
                            state, in reply, that the facts communicated therein have been made
                            known to the Secretary of the Navy.</p>
                <p>The undersigned offers to Mr. Tassara assurances of his highest
                            consideration.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>W. HUNTER,</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Señor Don <hi rend="smallcaps">Gabriel Garcia y Tassara</hi>, <hi rend="italic">&amp;c., &amp;c., Washington.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
